			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-1350810">
									

<p>I've had this sitting and rotting in my text folder for months and months, and felt that it was time to put it up. I still have misgivings about revealing things like backstory and such, even though i'm not, in ANY way, saying this is &quot;canon&quot;. I feel things are more scary when they just&#8230;happen, like a fire or a tornado&#8230;just the end result of a random universe. Still, it was fun to write&#8230;</p>
