														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-1352153">
									

<p>I'm reminded of a comment made by Isaac Asimov. He worried sometimes for new science fiction writers, who looked up on the high tower, and saw all these great, well-rooted writers, who just would not <em>die</em> and leave some bloody room for the new folks. I hope I inspire more then I intimidate&#8230;really, i'm just a fanboy at heart. A prolific fanboy, but a fanboy all the same.</p>

